    "body": "Sorry for the late answer.\r\n\r\nI'm not sure to understand the last question.\r\n\r\nAssuming you're using InstantSearch.js v2, you can style the CSS class to move the price values:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n.ais-range-slider--tooltip {\r\n  margin-top: 50px;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou can change the `margin-top` value at your convenience.",
